rclone
  Conductor supervises and presents the rclone binary; it does not reimplement
  rclone. When a build distributes the pinned rclone binary, that binary remains
  under its own license (rclone is MIT-licensed; verify at the pinned version).
  Conductor's Apache-2.0 license does not override rclone's license. The pinned
  version and its license notice are recorded with the release.
  https://rclone.org  —  https://github.com/rclone/rclone

