Third-party Go modules
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This software depends on third-party Go modules, each under its own license, as
recorded in go.mod / go.sum. Notable direct dependencies include:

  github.com/wailsapp/wails/v2        MIT
  github.com/BurntSushi/toml          MIT
